@NODE intro "Introduction"
@{u}Introduction@{uu}

   This is a simple door which lets your callers make up a story! The idea is
that a caller can add to the story, after he or she has read it and understood
the storyline, so you get a good story going and everybody who uses it decides
the story line.

   Note: Please don't start doing a Star Trek story cos I think we need NEW
ideas somewhat, and Star Trek gets very depressing when people keep on and ON
about it!!

@{u}Requirements@{uu}

MAX's BBS v1.52+.

@ENDNODE


