@NODE History "History"
@{u}History@{uu}

1.0 - Initial release. No bugs yet ;)

----- Renamed to KewlStory, version numbers start again *grin*! :) -----

1.0 - Renamed to KewlStory. Partially fixed display bug, now
      allowed upto 71 chars per line.
      New edit menu options.
      Now able to display ANSI menu instead of built in one.
      Maxs/paragon switch.
      
1.1 - Made docs into guide.
      Removed internal crap-menu, you must have a Menu.text now.
      Added all colours to saving, removed centering function.
      Fixed up some bugs and cleaned up code.
      Re-wrote code using the KewlDoors extension by Niki Murkett.
      Optimised and improved code, shrank source code length.
      Made the editor better, and now accepts upto 75 characters per line.
       
1.2 - Fixed security problems with MAX's Pro 2.

@ENDNODE

